<h4>How to calibrate your phone?</h4>
If your phone is not in the listed the application, the application could still
work but the measurements will likely be significantly less accurate.
<br/>If you have access to a sound level meter, you can contribute by calibrating
your phone model yourself by following the instructions in <a href="http://docs.google.com/View?id=dchqdm7_298gxfb9pd9">this document</a>. Please send us your results so we can integrate them in the program so the whole NoiseTube community can benefit from your effort.